### YANG Ailin_推荐系统＋group communication_COMM7320project

•	What is the specific topic and MCPP you are interested in?
A social networking system allows users to establish connections with other users by using recommendation system to push same 
contents .For example, users can view the Wechat publish passages displaying the number of their friends who had read the 
articles .And a relative function is named ’Top Stories’ in Wechat, users can receive the recommended articles computed by the 
algorithm considering those articles that users’ friend would read.  

•	What concepts and/or theories will be covered?
群体传播理论(Group Communication)
在群體交流中形成的一致性意見會產生群體傾向，群體傾向意味著無形的壓力，這種群體壓力能夠改變群體中個別人的不同意見，從而導致從眾行為。

